<span id="freeTextContainer668439716480156158">On page 100. I gave it a try but, unfortunately, I have to stop reading this novel. It&apos;s just too hard to read the Scottish dialect in almost every sentence for a Dutch person like myself.</span>
  <span id="freeText668439716480156158" style="display:none">On page 100. I gave it a try but, unfortunately, I have to stop reading this novel. It's just too hard to read the Scottish dialect in almost every sentence for a Dutch person like myself.</span>
