<div id="review_2522035327" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2522035327" />
    <a title="Reading Badger" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/72386518-reading-badger"><img alt="Reading Badger" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1507817864p2/72386518.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2522035327?book_show_action=true">Sep 07, 2018</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Reading Badger" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Reading Badger" href="/user/show/72386518-reading-badger">Reading Badger</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2522035327" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer4412608047313696734">It is no surprise to you that I am a devoted Irvine Welsh fan. For me, every book he releases is like a new series from my favourite show. The first book I read was Trainspotting, and I fell in love with the characters, the atmosphere, everything. So when I heard that a new book with Renton, Sick Boy, Spud and Begbie was up for grabs, it was on my pre-order list right away.<br/><br/>The story left off at the end of Porno, whith Begbie trying to kill Renton, and Renton scamming Sick Boy out of a lot of mon</span>
  <span id="freeText4412608047313696734" style="display:none">It is no surprise to you that I am a devoted Irvine Welsh fan. For me, every book he releases is like a new series from my favourite show. The first book I read was Trainspotting, and I fell in love with the characters, the atmosphere, everything. So when I heard that a new book with Renton, Sick Boy, Spud and Begbie was up for grabs, it was on my pre-order list right away.<br /><br />The story left off at the end of Porno, whith Begbie trying to kill Renton, and Renton scamming Sick Boy out of a lot of money. Dead man’s trousers begins in 2015, with Renton, now a successful DJ Manager, when he encounters Begbie (now a big time artist in LA, with a beautiful wife and two kids) on a transatlantic flight. Rather than the death threats he expected, Renton finds Begbie with a zen-like attitude.<br /><br />Read our review: <a target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow" href="https://readingbadger.club/2018/09/07/dead-mens-trousers-book-review/">https://readingbadger.club/2018/09/07...</a><br /></span>
