  <span id="freeText15874047570203372577" style="display:none">The boys are back in the toon and they embark on likely capers with a dark undertow. It's like catching up with old pals that you are happy to hear about, their exploits still raise a smile, but that you are very glad not to see anymore. It's a very entertaining read especially Sick Boy's antics - a pint with him might be the best fun but as a female of the species and to quote the man himself, I wouldn't go near him with yours!!</span>
