<div id="review_4187602256" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/4187602256" />
    <a title="Guy Portman" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/11566536-guy-portman"><img alt="Guy Portman" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1539458477p2/11566536.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/4187602256?book_show_action=true">Aug 20, 2021</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Guy Portman" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Guy Portman" href="/user/show/11566536-guy-portman">Guy Portman</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Hardcover 9781612197555" href="/book/show/40068450-dead-men-s-trousers">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/11566536-guy-portman?shelf=transgressive">transgressive</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/11566536-guy-portman?shelf=humour">humour</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer4187602256" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer8303974939617161461">The &apos;Trainspotting&apos; crew are back for another adventure. These days Mark Renton is a successful manager of DJs. Begbie is a famous artist, living the dream in California. Sick Boy hasn’t changed much. He now runs an escort agency in London. Affable and gullible Spud is still a drug-using dropout. <br/><br/>Their reunion is tense, as the friends have a chequered history and considerable resentment remains. If Begbie hasn’t ditched his psychopathic ways as he claims, things could get nasty. <br/><br/>This work of tra</span>
  <span id="freeText8303974939617161461" style="display:none">The 'Trainspotting' crew are back for another adventure. These days Mark Renton is a successful manager of DJs. Begbie is a famous artist, living the dream in California. Sick Boy hasn’t changed much. He now runs an escort agency in London. Affable and gullible Spud is still a drug-using dropout. <br /><br />Their reunion is tense, as the friends have a chequered history and considerable resentment remains. If Begbie hasn’t ditched his psychopathic ways as he claims, things could get nasty. <br /><br />This work of transgressive fiction is infused with humour. The action takes place in Scotland and America. Themes include drugs, sex, drinking and music. The familiar band of reprobates, hilarious antics and incisive Leith vernacular more than compensate for the dearth of plot. 'Dead Men’s Trousers' will appeal to fans of Irvine Welsh.</span>
  <a data-text-id="8303974939617161461" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


